From a0e41c046584d0e47edd4f976c2f0224c4919b4d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Gaoyang Zhang <younglobalization@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Jul 2026 01:45:19 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] vendor(openclaw): surface failed Feishu quote reads

Why:
- quoted-message API, empty-response, and parse failures collapse to null, so agents mistake employee replies for complete context
- quoted-message GETs should use bounded transient and rate-limit retries before exposing a terminal failure
- merged-forward quotes return a non-JSON root plus interactive child cards, so selecting only the root loses escalation IDs

Removal:
- drop when upstream retries and diagnoses quoted-message reads, preserves an explicit unavailable-quote marker, and expands merged-forward interactive child content

Tests:
- extensions/feishu/src/send.test.ts
- extensions/feishu/src/bot.test.ts
- apps/desktop/src/cs-bridge/vendor-feishu-escalation-quote.sentinel.test.ts
